# Build stage
FROM maven:3.9-eclipse-temurin-21-alpine AS builder

WORKDIR /build

COPY pom.xml .
RUN mvn dependency:go-offline -B

COPY src ./src
RUN mvn package -DskipTests -B

# Runtime stage
FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine

RUN apk add --no-cache \
    curl \
    fontconfig \
    ttf-dejavu \
    ca-certificates \
    && rm -rf /var/cache/apk/*

# Download AWS RDS and Azure certificates
RUN mkdir -p /tmp/certs && \
    curl -fsSL https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/global/global-bundle.pem -o /tmp/certs/aws-rds-global-bundle.pem && \
    curl -fsSL https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootG2.crt.pem -o /tmp/certs/azure-digicert-root.pem

# Import certificates into Java truststore
RUN keytool -importcert \
    -alias aws-rds-global-root-1 \
    -file /tmp/certs/aws-rds-global-bundle.pem \
    -keystore $JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts \
    -storepass changeit \
    -noprompt && \
    keytool -importcert \
    -alias azure-digicert-root \
    -file /tmp/certs/azure-digicert-root.pem \
    -keystore $JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts \
    -storepass changeit \
    -noprompt && \
    rm -rf /tmp/certs

RUN addgroup -g 1001 app && \
    adduser -u 1001 -G app -D -h /app app

WORKDIR /app

COPY --from=builder --chown=app:app /build/target/*.jar /app/app.jar

USER app

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=10s --start-period=60s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -fsSL http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

CMD ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
